title: 12: The Fast Food Episode: Part 2
itunes:title: The Fast Food Episode: Part 2
description: We’re back with FAST FOOD: PART 2! In this episode, Lisa hands out the FAST FOOD AWARDS, answers an ASK HG about an iconic FAST FOOD dessert, and reveals the FAST FOOD she’s LOVING this week! In addition, the HG crew tries new products from Dunkin Donuts, Starbucks, and Taco Bell. Start your engines, because after this episode, you’ll wanna make a beeline for your favorite drive-thru window! [hungry-girl.com/fastfood](hungry-girl.com/fastfood)
